                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">耳機大廠 Jabra 再次推出新款真無線藍牙耳機，Jabra Elite 8 Active。過去 Jabra 的真無線藍牙耳機口碑都不俗，尤其受著重低頻的用家歡迎。今次推出的 Elite 8 Active，小編試完覺得 Elite 8 Active 承傳了 Jabra 的低頻表現，而高頻方面亦有進步，價錢方面屬中價位。</p><p><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" class="size-medium wp-image-1197878 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09844-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09844-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09844-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09844-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09844-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09844-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1197879 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09904-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09904-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09904-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09904-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09904-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09904-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Jabra Elite 8 Active</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>設計簡單 </strong><strong>3</strong><strong>種顏色選擇 </strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">Jabra Elite 8 Active 的設計及外觀簡約，前方有電量提示，機盒用上了磨砂，手感不錯，不易留下指紋等污漬。機底位置有個 USB-C 充電位。Jabra Elite 8 Active 共有 3 款顏色選擇，小編拿到的是深灰色，另外有深藍色，及比較突出焦糖色，小編覺得焦糖色比較特別。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1197846 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09842-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09842-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09842-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09842-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09842-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09842-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Jabra Elite 8 Active</p><h2><strong>機身只重</strong><strong> 5 克，佩戴感舒適</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">一如既往，Jabra 系列的真無線藍牙耳機都會隨機附送 3 對耳膠，及 1 條耳機同色的 USB-C 充電線。Jabra Elite 8 Active 繼續使用入耳式設計，機身質感是液態矽橡膠，主打運動時使用，官方的耳機機身重量為 5 克，小編戴了半天未感不適，感覺非常穩陣，不輕易掉下，加上其防水防塵等級為 IP68，即是完全防塵及可浸入超過一米的水中，用家可安心帶住做運動。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1197858 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09852-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09852-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09852-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09852-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09852-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09852-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Jabra Elite 8 Active 隨機附送 3 對耳膠，及 1 條耳機同色的 USB-C 充電線</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1197847 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09850-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09850-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09850-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09850-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09850-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09850-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲機身只重 5 克</p><h2><strong>Jabra Sound+ 可調 EQ</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">操控方面頗為簡單，單次按下右邊可播放及暫停音樂，單按左邊則是切換主動降噪或通透模式。Jabra 向來都有自家應用程式 Jabra Sound+，主要是用來調整主動降噪的程度、通透程度、EQ 等。當中主動降噪及通透都有 5 個程度選擇，如用家覺得有壓迫感或不適，可以自行調低主動降噪。通透程度則會放大外在聲量。EQ 方面就預設 6 項，若用家對 EQ 未有太多認識，想信足夠使用。高階的用家亦可自行調節。另外，Jabra Sound+ 提供了背景功能，用家可以當作背景音，即使不想聽音樂，也可以使用耳機專注工作，或達至放鬆的效果。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1197849 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2257-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2257-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2257-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2257.jpg 739w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2257-710x1536.jpg 710w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Jabra Sound+ 可切換 ANC，通透模式及純物理隔音</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1197848 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2258-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2258-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2258-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2258.jpg 739w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2258-710x1536.jpg 710w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ Jabra Sound+ 可調 EQ 及背景聲</p><h2>Active <strong>Hybird ANC 通話表現良好</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">Jabra Elite 8 Active 擁有 Active Hybird ANC，即是混合式主動降噪功能，雖然並非 Jabra 耳機中最強科技，但一足夠一般情況下使用。耳機內外均有收音咪，處理的噪音頻率比一般 ANC 還要闊。Jabra Elite 8 Active  通話表現良好，如果在室內通話並沒問題，室外可能偶爾會有風噪聲。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1197880 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09910-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09910-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09910-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09910-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09910-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09910-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1197850 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09847-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09847-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09847-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09847-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09847-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09847-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Jabra Elite 8 Active 擁有 Active Hybird ANC，足夠應付日常大多數環境</p><h2><strong>支援快速充電，充電 </strong>5 分鐘可用 1 小時</h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">續航力方面，開啟主動降噪後，滿電的 Jabra Elite 8 Active 可以連續使 8 小時，連耳機盒則可使用長達 32 小時，都足夠小編使用 3 日。而關閉主動降噪則更可分別使用 14 小時及 56 小時，續航力頗長。Jabra Elite 8 Active 如其他耳機般，支援快速充電，只要充電 5 分鐘，即可使用 1 小時。總充電時間為  3 小時。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1197851 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09856-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09856-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09856-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09856-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09856-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09856-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Jabra Elite 8 Active 支援快速充電，只要充電 5 分鐘，即可使用 1 小時</p><h2><strong>Spatial Sound 空間感更闊，睇戲聽歌更爽</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">Jabra Elite 8 Active 與 Dolby 合作，加入了 Spatial Sound 的功能，令用家有另外的感受，可聽到更瞭闊的音場。小編認為適合用來看電影及聽現場音樂。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1197852 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2259-470x580.jpg" alt="" width="470" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2259-470x580.jpg 470w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2259-730x900.jpg 730w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2259-768x947.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2259.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 470px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Spatial Sound 可令用家聽到更瞭闊的音場</p><h2><strong>高頻人聲有驚喜</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">小編在 iPhone 上使用 Moov 播放陳柏宇的《尊嚴》，分別是錄音版本及 Fight For ___ Live in Hong Conilseum 演唱會現場版本。小編覺得唱片版本關閉 Spatial Sound 更為適合，高頻及人聲聲音更突出，適合喜歡聽 Vocal 的用家。而現場版本開啟 Spatial Sound 可能更好，小編頗喜歡 Spatial Sound 帶來的現場感。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1197853 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2261-313x580.jpg" alt="" width="313" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2261-313x580.jpg 313w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2261-485x900.jpg 485w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2261-768x1425.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2261.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 313px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲陳柏宇《尊嚴》（錄音版本）</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1197854 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2260-310x580.jpg" alt="" width="310" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2260-310x580.jpg 310w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2260-481x900.jpg 481w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2260-768x1438.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2260-821x1536.jpg 821w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2260.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 310px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲陳柏宇《尊嚴》（Fight For ___ Live in Hong Conilseum 演唱會現場版本）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">再聽聽 Mr. 的《邊城》，不論歌手聲底厚薄，似乎 Elite 8 Active 都演繹得不錯，人聲依舊突出。低頻亦足夠份量及下潛力。但《邊城》始終是樂隊音樂，編曲比較複雜，要求耳機的分析力高，以中價定位的耳機來説，表現合格。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1197855 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2262-313x580.jpg" alt="" width="313" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2262-313x580.jpg 313w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2262-485x900.jpg 485w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2262-768x1425.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2262.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 313px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Mr. 《邊城》</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Elite 8 Active 與過去的 Jabra 耳機聲音上有點分別，除了如以往一樣著重低音外，高頻方面都下了苦功，令人聲高頻更出色。整體來説，Elite 8 Active 適合收聽流行曲。</p><h2>Spatial Sound <strong>串流播片 </strong><strong>置身現場</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">小編使用 Apple TV 串流觀看《全面入侵》（Invasion）第一季第一集，未有感到延遲，音色方面造得不俗，開啟 Spatial Sound，可使音場更闊，更迫真，彷如置身現場。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1197856 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-05-at-4.54.31-PM-694x384.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="384" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-05-at-4.54.31-PM-694x384.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-05-at-4.54.31-PM-1280x709.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-05-at-4.54.31-PM-768x425.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-05-at-4.54.31-PM-1536x850.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-05-at-4.54.31-PM-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《全面入侵》（Invasion）第一季第一集</p><h2><strong>總結： </strong>Spatial Sound 新體驗 <strong>高頻</strong><strong>音色出眾</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">Elite 8 Active 的音色比以往的 Jabra 耳機更重視人聲，使其整體音色提高了一個層次。Spatial Sound 亦令用家有多個選擇，視乎情況和喜好使用。整體而言，Elite 8 Active 適合運動用，亦適合喜愛聽高頻人聲的用家。</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

